## 6. Tag Editing Touchpoints (Summary)

Users can manage tags from two places:

| Location | What they can do |
|----------|-----------------|
| **Tag Manager page** | View all tags, rename, merge, delete, see prompt counts |
| **Manage Prompts tab** (inline) | Add/remove tags on individual prompts via popup, create new tags on the spot |

Both are synced — changes in either location update the same underlying tag system.

